== Django backend for easy authentication with Facebook == 



1) Create an app on facebook and activate sandbox mode - this will let you use http requests - and change canvas URL to http://127.0.0.1:8000/
2) Change everything on your settings.py that is inside <> to your configuration

TEMPLATE_DIRS = (
    '<YOUR-DJANGO-PROJECT>/django_fukinbook/templates',
)

AUTHENTICATION_BACKENDS = (
    '<YOUR-DJANGO-PROJECT>.django_fukinbook.backends.FacebookBackend',
    'django.contrib.auth.backends.ModelBackend',
)

INSTALLED_APPS = (
    'django.contrib.auth',
    'django.contrib.contenttypes',
    'django.contrib.sessions',
    'django.contrib.sites',
    'django.contrib.messages',
    'django.contrib.staticfiles',
    'django_fukinbook',
    'django.contrib.admin',
)

FACEBOOK_APP_ID = '<YOUR-APP-ID>'
FACEBOOK_APP_SECRET = '<YOUR-APP-SECRET>'
FACEBOOK_REDIRECT_URI = 'http://127.0.0.1:8000/'
FACEBOOK_APP_SCOPE = ','.join(['user_relationships', 
                               'friends_birthday']) # You can change to facebook scopes you want to use

GRAPH_API_URL = 'https://graph.facebook.com/'
MAIN_URL = '/canvas/' # This is the index of your facebook app

3) Change your urls.py

from django.conf.urls.defaults import patterns, include, url
from django.contrib import admin
admin.autodiscover()

urlpatterns = patterns('',
    url(r'^login/', 'django_fukinbook.views.login'),
    url(r'^canvas/', 'django_fukinbook.views.canvas'),
    url(r'^admin/', include(admin.site.urls)),
)

4) Optional: If you want to DEBUG fukinbook, add those loggers:
    'loggers': {
        '': {
            'handlers': ['console'],
            'level': 'DEBUG',
            'propagate': True
        },
        'django.db.backends': { # Does not log SQL queries
            'handlers': ['console'],
            'level': 'ERROR',
            'propagate': False,
        },
    },

5) python manage.py syncdb
6) Go to browser and type http://127.0.0.1:8000/

We started this project from http://djangosnippets.org/snippets/2065/
Thanks to http://djangosnippets.org/users/barnardo/
